These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite, mirinda
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, cricket, baseball
1. the person who's sport is cricket is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | sprite | mirinda   |
| Sport      | volleyball    | cricket  | baseball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, soy-milk, mirinda
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, american, thai
1. the japanese is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the american is on the far left##1
3. the american is the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | sprite     | mirinda      |
| Nationality   | american | japanese | thai |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, almond-milk
There 3 different types of food: blueberry, lime, kale
1. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person eating lime##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person eating kale##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person eating lime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | fanta | almond-milk  | juice       |
| Food       | blueberry     | lime | kale |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, broccoli, mango
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, photography, traveling
1. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Food    | mango    | broccoli     | eggplant |
| Hobby   | traveling | fishing | photography     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, cat, lizard
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, roller, skateboard
1. the person driving the roller is the owner of the lizard##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Pet         | cat | chinchilla     | lizard |
| Transport   | skateboard        | motorbike | roller    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There 3 different types of food: carrot, apricot, peas
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, tram, scooter
1. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
3. the person eating peas is the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Food        | peas | carrot      | apricot  |
| Transport   | bus       | tram | scooter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, blues, d&b
3 different pets are kept: turtle, frog, guinea-pig
1. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of folk##1
2. the fan of blues is the owner of the frog##1
3. the owner of the turtle is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b      | folk     | blues    |
| Pet           | turtle | guinea-pig | frog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
