2. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
3. the person eating plum is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Food    | raspberry | cucumber | plum      |
| Hobby   | filmmaking     | magic-tricks | puzzles |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
