.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, fanta
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, fantasy, crime
1. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person watching crime movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage      | iced-tea   | juice    | fanta    |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | musical | crime |

