.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-13::.
There 3 different types of food: pepper, broccoli, pineapple
The people have 3 different jobs:  nurse, designer, engineer
1. the designer is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
2. the person eating pineapple is in the middle##1
3. the nurse is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food   | pepper     | pineapple   | broccoli     |
| Job    | engineer | designer | nurse |

