3 different pets are kept: turtle, goat, snake
1. the owner of the snake is on the left of the social-worker##1
2. the social-worker is on the left of the lawyer##1
3. the lawyer is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |       2        |      3      |
| Job   | pilot    | social-worker | lawyer |
