.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, water, tea
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, indie, r&b
1. the person drinking water is on the far right##1
2. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person drinking water##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the right of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Beverage      | mirinda  | tea | water  |
| Music-Genre   | indie | r&b   | techno |

