The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, soccer, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person eating lettuce is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
3. the person eating peach is on the right of the person eating plum##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Food    | plum | peach   | lettuce        |
| Sport   | soccer    | rowing | snowboarding |

