.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-19::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, reading, collecting
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, hip-hop, techno
1. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of techno##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is the fan of techno##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | reading | collecting |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | techno     | hip-hop  |

