.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: watermelon, peas, artichoke
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, swimming, rowing
1. the person who's sport is swimming is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
3. the person eating peas is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Food    | artichoke | watermelon       | peas  |
| Sport   | rowing  | swimming | skiing |

 